The '''Bondum language''', '''''Bondum Dom''''', is a [[Dogon language]] spoken in [[Mali]]. It is closest to [[Dogul Dogon]], though not enough for mutual intelligibility. Dialects are ''Kindjim'' and ''Nadjamba''.

