'''Kitty C. Calavita''' is an American criminologist, focusing in sociology of law, criminology, immigration, criminal justice and inequality, currently the Chancellor's Professor Emerita at [[University of California, Irvine]] and an Elected Fellow of the [[American Political and Social Science Society]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aapss.org/fellows-of-the-academy/#1470762859183-eb2362e8-b290 |title=Fellows |publisher=aapss.org |accessdate=May 10, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://faculty.sites.uci.edu/kccalavi/ |title=Kitty Calavita |publisher=uci.edu |accessdate=May 10, 2017}}</ref>

